This page indexes every update [[V Rising]] has received, newest first. Major updates have their own articles with curated notes: [[Patch 1.1]] (''Invaders of Oakveil''), [[Patch 1.0]], [[Secrets of Gloomrot]], [[Bloodfeast]] and the [[Early Access Release]].

[[File:Stunlock Studios Logo.png|25px|link=Stunlock Studios]] [[Stunlock Studios]] has [https://blog.stunlock.com/dev-update-32-the-next-era/ announced] that there will be no more major expansions to the game, only intermittent balance and bug fixes as the studio shifts its focus to developing a '''new game''' also set in the world of [[V Rising]].

